<i>Kenapa para kuda jatuh sakit...</i>

924
01:10:12,549 --> 01:10:14,092
<i>Eunseom menggantikanku.</i>

925
01:10:14,176 --> 01:10:15,969
<i>Kenapa aku tak bisa lakukan hal sama.</i>

926
01:10:16,052 --> 01:10:17,429
<i>Jika pedang itu terungkap,</i>

927
01:10:17,512 --> 01:10:19,639
<i>tapi aku tak tahu apa misinya,</i>

928
01:10:19,723 --> 01:10:21,433
<i>apa itu artinya aku bukan Aramun?</i>

929
01:10:22,184 --> 01:10:23,310
<i>Tagon berhalusinasi.</i>

930
01:10:23,393 --> 01:10:25,812
Kau harus membunuh semua orang sekarang.

931
01:10:26,563 --> 01:10:28,064
<i>Aku tak akan dibodohi</i>

932
01:10:28,148 --> 01:10:29,608
<i>olehmu,</i>

933
01:10:29,691 --> 01:10:31,276
<i>atau ramalan itu.</i>

